-- Travis Perkins Agrees Cash, Shares Offer With BSS of 353.5 Cents a Share
-- Howard Mustoe
-- 2010-07-05T06:05:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/travis-perkins-agrees-cash-shares-offer-with-bss-of-353-5-cents-a-share.html

          
          
             Travis Perkins Plc said it and BSS
Group Plc have reached an agreement for Travis Perkins to buy
BSS. The company will offer 232.91 pence cash for each BSS
share, as well as 0.2608 new Travis Perkins shares.  
 That values each BSS share at 435.8 pence, based on a
Travis Perkins closing price of 754.4 pence on July 2, Travis
Perkins  said.  
          
          


  


        